- [ ] GitHub repo Settings → Pages shows "Your site is live"

**Manual Verification**:
- [ ] Navigate to `https://radoxtech.github.io/hipocalc`
- [ ] Page loads without 404
- [ ] Console has no errors about base path

**Commit**: YES
